core::slice::<impl [T]>::iter_mut.doc:
Returns an iterator that allows modifying each value.

The iterator yields all items from start to end.

# Examples

```
let x = &mut [1, 2, 4];
for elem in x.iter_mut() {
    *elem += 2;
}
assert_eq!(x, &[3, 4, 6]);
```

